      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified+1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.6/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/c215b106-1623-11e5-a261-5254006e85c2).  Ran 17 tests.  No failures.",
